snippet.title: BipBop 2 gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for BipBop 2, Dos PC game produced by S&M Software in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/bipbop-2/5878/
BipBop 2 is an excellent game to prove your skill, you must destroy several square with a ball.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
